description: Atlanta foodies are being treated to a deliciously different smoked BBQ experience, thanks to Exotic Que and their tasty tropical flavors. Out of their fully equipped trailer with a smoker, grill, 3 televisions, and a stereo sound system, they’re serving up a succulent selection of smoked pulled pork, pork ribs, beef brisket, turkey legs, and chicken. Their acclaimed sides include crisp coleslaw, potato salad, and exotic baked beans. Come on out to Exotic Que real soon, join in the festivities, and delight in these non-traditional BBQ dishes!
name: Exotic Que
